Even if I have to work all night tonight, I'll make sure to finish translating all these materials

17
00:01:43,885 --> 00:01:47,620
and then make a clean break with you.

18
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:57,520
Senior? What are you doing here?

19
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,860
You said you're working overtime,

20
00:01:58,860 --> 00:02:01,960
so I thought you must be hungry. I brought you some food.

21
00:02:03,620 --> 00:02:06,000
Thank you, Senior.

22
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,420
Fried chicken!

23
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:11,000
Do you have to finish translating all these documents tonight?

24
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,680
Yes.

25
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:15,420
The sooner I finish, the sooner I can break free from Exploitative Gu.

26
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:18,020
I must finish it all tonight.

27
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:20,680
Let me help you.

28
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,960
No need.

29
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:25,100
How can I trouble President Du with my little part-time job?

30
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:26,680
I get your point.

31
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:30,660
You think I can't help you because I don't know French, right?

32
00:02:30,660 --> 00:02:33,140
Did I make it that obvious?

33
00:02:33,140 --> 00:02:37,980
Even though I don't understand French, I can still help you proofread documents and staple them, or something.

34
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:40,840
Anyway, it's definitely faster than you doing it alone.

35
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:46,760
Do you remember back when we stayed up all night working on experiments together?

36
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:49,240
Speaking of which, I actually quite miss those old days.

37
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,700
Rather than saying it's you bothering me,

38
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:56,980
it's more like you're taking me back to our university days, and letting me feel young again.

39
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:03,280
Okay. Thanks in advance then, Senior.

40
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,280
We don't need to be so polite.

41
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:09,660
Come on. Let's see if we can still work together

42
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:13,240
as perfectly as we did before.

43
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:39,140
This is what you asked me to translate yesterday.

44
00:03:39,140 --> 00:03:41,560
I'm finished. Please check it and confirm.

45
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,940
So fast?

46
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:54,500
Are you sure you're not trying to deceive me?

47
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:57,980
You can check it as you wish.

48
00:03:57,980 --> 00:04:02,820
How's this possible? This isn't a task that can be finished in just one night.

49
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:07,620
Yesterday, Senior stayed up all night with me and helped me finish it.

50
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:09,580
Du Yuncheng?

51
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:13,280
You did the translation with him?

52
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:18,620
So you two stayed in the lab all night?

53
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:21,720
Yes. Is there a problem?

54
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:26,700
Su Wei'an, I let you return to the lab

55
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:30,680
because I wanted you to work, not to date inside of it.

56
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,800
Who gave you permission to let an outsider into my lab?

57
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:37,040
Who's dating in the lab? Can you not talk nonsense?

58
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:42,720
I told you before. Without my permission, no one is allowed into my lab.

59
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,520
Are you ignoring what I say?

60
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:46,540
Come on, man. Can you be reasonable?

61
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:49,160
I helped you translate materials, yet I still get scolded by you.

62
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,940
If Du Yuncheng is an outsider, then I'm even more so.

63
00:04:51,940 --> 00:04:54,700
If you're in a bad mood, go scold someone else. Find someone who upsets you.

64
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,820
Why are you losing your temper with me?

65
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,840
I'm not losing my temper with you.

66
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,260
Never mind, I don't care.

67
00:05:01,260 --> 00:05:03,380
Anyway, my translation work is done.

68
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:06,180
Please check it immediately and give me the final payment.

69
00:05:06,180 --> 00:05:08,940
Starting today, I don't need to come to work anymore.

70
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:12,900
And, even more so, I don't need to accept your oppression anymore.

71
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:32,440
You don't have to go to the lab to work today?

72
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:35,040
I worked all night yesterday.

73
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,920
Do you want me to work myself to death?

74
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,480
I was just asking.

75
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:41,700
What? Are you angry? Are you having your period?

76
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:44,900
I think Gu Yunzheng is having his period.

77
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:53,520

78
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,700
So much money?

79
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,700

80
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:05,920
I think he can have his period more often.

81
00:06:11,540 --> 00:06:12,940
Miss Su.

82
00:06:12,940 --> 00:06:16,100
An? What are you doing here?

83
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:18,500
You... You two...

84
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,160
This is my current and only boyfriend.

85
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:22,620
This is my current and only boyfriend.

86
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:31,200
He's your current and only boyfriend?

87
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:33,240
What about Gu Yunzheng?

88
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,140
Dr. Gu...

89
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:36,560
He doesn't really count as an ex-boyfriend.

90
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:40,520
He's more like a missed target, I guess.

91
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:45,080
So, Dr. Gu rejected you?

92
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,920
Yes, he did.

93
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:50,580
But he can be seen as the first failure I've ever encountered in life.

94
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:53,820
My darling, you're gorgeous.

95
00:06:55,180 --> 00:06:57,080
We'll get going then.

96
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:10,000
What's all this about?

97
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:14,720
It turns out Gu Yunzheng didn't have a change of heart.

98
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:17,580
He's always had you in his heart.

99
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:21,560
Then has he been acting all this time?

100
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:24,180
But why would he do that?

101
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:26,100
 There's a herbal restaurant that opened near the hospital.

102
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:29,900
 I just took my girlfriend to try it, and I brought some back.

103
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:32,140
 Do you want to try some of this soup?

104
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:34,980
 Are you sure this is leftover food?

105
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:38,363
 Interpreter Su, please open it and try some.

106
00:07:38,363 --> 00:07:41,180
 If it tastes good, tell me. I want to give it to my girlfriend.

107
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:45,960
 Dr. Gu, I'm your translator, not a guinea pig.

108
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,800
 I'll add to your pay.

109
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,240

110
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:56,480
He deliberately gave me more money because he's afraid I won't accept it.

111
00:07:57,931 --> 00:07:59,771
My tummy hurts.

112
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,500
Jiang...

113
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:05,940
Jiang Muying.

114
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:16,620
You're already very familiar with this surgery, right?

115
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:22,670
You're done with the surgery, Boss?

116
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:26,480
Why did you choose this approach?

117
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:29,100
Is there a problem? I still have time to make changes.

118
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:32,520
I mean, why did you choose this less common approach

119
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:35,500
instead of the more reliable pterional approach?

120
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:38,320
That girl is only 17 years old.

121
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,900
She told me she likes singing and dancing.

122
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:42,860
And that she wants to major in performing arts.

123
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:44,440
Her tumor isn't very big.

124
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:50,020
I want to protect her hearing and facial nerves, so I chose the approach with the smallest incision.

125
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:53,240
With a smaller incision, the surgical field is also more limited.

126
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,150
The operation will be more complex.

127
00:08:55,150 --> 00:09:01,160
If that's the case, I'll just peel it layer by layer, until it's all clean.

128
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:03,200
Aren't you afraid?

129
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,040
I am.

130
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:09,919
But Su Wei'an reminded me.

131
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:14,000
She said, when a doctor is operating, they should be pure and selfless.

132
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:18,280
Since they picked up the scalpel, they must provide the best treatment for the patient.

133
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,200
Su Wei'an said that?

134
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,000
Yes.

135
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:28,160
That day, Dr. Li told me to choose the approach I'm most confident in to overcome my psychological barriers.

136
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:31,240
But I still agree with what Su Wei'an said.

137
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,620
She's pretty awesome.

138
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:37,180
If she hadn't dropped out, she would've become a very skilled surgeon.

139
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:38,960
She'll come back.

140
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,540
What's the matter, Boss?

141
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,720
She didn't even accept money?

142
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:57,060
That doesn't seem like Su Wei'an's style.

143
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:02,940
We're done for, Boss.

144
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:04,480
Jiang Jiang said she gave away the secret.

145
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:08,920
She said Su Wei'an found out about you using a fake girlfriend to deceive her.

146
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,510
An An.

147
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:28,080
Are you planning to go back to the hospital to work?

148
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:36,920
If the new drug doesn't go to market, what are you going to do in the future?

149
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:41,080
Auntie, this isn't something I should worry about.

150
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:43,960
Why is it not?

151
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:48,580
You also carry the gene that causes this disease.

152
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:55,860
That report can only deceive your mom.

153
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,760
There's nothing I can hide from you.

154
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:05,040
I can tell. You and that Dr. Gu like each other.

155
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:07,020
No way.

156
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:14,320
My mom already said that Dr. Gu is excellent, and I'm not good enough for him.

157
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:26,822
I've noticed that after stopping the medication, my reactions have been more intense than before.

158
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:32,160
I often can't control my emotions.

159
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:35,180
I feel like I'm not the same person as I used to be.

160
00:11:38,660 --> 00:11:41,940
I don't want you to become like me.

161
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:47,140
I hope that you live with even more courage than I did, without any regrets.

162
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:49,300
I hope that you live with even more courage than I did, without any regrets.

163
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:55,580
Auntie, I'm doing great now.

164
00:11:55,580 --> 00:11:57,580
I have no regrets.

165
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:04,420
As long as our family is together and happy every day, that's enough for me.

166
