167
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:59,720
 This handwriting... It's Gu Yunzheng.

168
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,480
Mom.

169
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:16,860
Where did this notebook come from?

170
00:13:16,860 --> 00:13:20,480
When I went to the hospital that day to pick up medicine, Dr. Gu gave it to me.

171
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:24,520
He's quite scrupulous. He wrote this personally, right?

172
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,760
I'm going to bed. You should sleep early too.

173
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:32,480
Go to sleep.

174
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:42,040
 Look, Su Wei'an.

175
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:46,380
 You even did extra data calculations for me and found so many papers to cite.

176
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:49,000
 You've never given up your passion for medicine.

177
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,100
 These habits of medical students...

178
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:54,400
 You've kept them even after being away from school for four years.

179
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:57,520
 Why do you always say one thing but mean another?

180
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:07,830

181
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:12,725
 You can resist, but I won't give up.

182
00:14:29,020 --> 00:14:32,140
Do you really want to distance yourself from me that much?

183
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:34,700
You won't even eat the cookies I bought.

184
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:55,860
Su Wei'an, you're really...

185
00:14:57,760 --> 00:15:01,020
really a kid who says one thing and means another.

