Hello, Senior.

201
00:17:09,540 --> 00:17:12,620
It's so late. What's the matter?

202
00:17:12,620 --> 00:17:14,580
I just finished dinner with a client.

203
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:16,740
Coincidentally, it's near your bar.

204
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:18,700
I want to watch you perform.

205
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:22,160
 I didn't go to the bar today. I had something else to take care of.

206
00:17:24,120 --> 00:17:25,440
Really?

207
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:29,100
That's okay then. I'll have a couple of drinks by myself.

208
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:30,940
I'll treat you next time we go to the bar.

209
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:34,000
Thank you for staying up all night translating with me.

210
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,660
 No problem.

211
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:40,040
 - By the way, I have a friend—  
- Senior, I have to hang up now.

212
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:01,420
So now you know.

213
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:03,940
I don't have a girlfriend.

214
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:05,630
I got it.

215
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:09,000
But it has nothing to do with me.

216
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:14,400
Don't you want to ask me why I did that?

217
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:19,820
Maybe you had too much money and wanted me to help.

218
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:24,380
Or maybe you've been too bored lately and wanted to make fun of me.

219
00:18:24,380 --> 00:18:26,480
How am I supposed to know why?

220
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:35,940
But Dr. Gu, your intelligence and talent being used in such petty tactics is really such a waste.

221
00:18:35,940 --> 00:18:40,220
If you have time to make such a notebook, why not do some more surgeries?

222
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:49,960
Is taking responsibility for my own patients also considered as playing tricks?

223
00:18:51,700 --> 00:18:58,420
If I hadn't played such tricks, Su Wei'an, you wouldn't face your true feelings at all.

224
00:18:58,420 --> 00:19:01,200
I know what my true feelings are. You don't need to remind me.

225
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:05,700
Su Wei'an, stop trying to be tough.

226
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:09,160
You clearly remember everything about us.

227
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:14,660
You're not as carefree in facing life as you claim to be.

228
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:20,900
Since you've chosen to think of me when you felt most helpless,

229
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:25,480
why are you pushing me away when things get better?

230
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:35,340
Sorry, Dr. Gu. I've caused you trouble.

231
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:38,160
How come you still don't get it?

232
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:41,400
I'm more than happy to be troubled by you.

233
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:56,060
Gu Yunzheng!

234
00:19:58,740 --> 00:20:03,500
Su Wei'an, I won't force you to make any decisions anymore.

235
00:20:04,380 --> 00:20:08,640
You have plenty of time to think it through carefully.

236
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:11,270
If one day you decide to look back,

237
00:20:11,900 --> 00:20:14,540
I'll always be behind you.

238
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:21,020
And the door of the lab is always open to you.

239
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:23,060
Genetic defects...

240
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:28,700
don't mean you can't have a normal life.

241
00:21:04,260 --> 00:21:10,170
♫  Rain falls on the deep blue sea  ♫

242
00:21:11,060 --> 00:21:15,420
Su Wei'an, you keep pushing me away like this.

243
00:21:15,420 --> 00:21:17,620
Have you ever thought that

244
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:24,520
if one day, an accident happens before the illness, and I were to leave you first,

